			<p>UV radiation in Australia can be particularly intense due to factors such as its proximity to the equator and the thinning ozone layer in the Southern Hemisphere. This makes sun safety especially important for children, whose skin is more sensitive to UV damage. Find age-appropriate tips and tricks to make sun safety fun and engaging for children.</p>
			@Html.ActionLink("Fun Sun Safety »", "FunSunSafety", "Home", null, new { @class = "btn btn-outline-dark" })
		</div>
		<div class="row-single-image">
